{"questionId":"12144","questionHtml":"<p>Perform a <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\chi ^2}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>χ</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> goodness of fit test at the 5% significance level. You should clearly state your hypotheses, the p-value, and your conclusion.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{H_0}\\,{\\text{:}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>H</mi>\n      <mn>0</mn>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>:</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;data is modeled by&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\\left( d \\right) = 9.7782{\\left( {1.7125} \\right)^d}\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>d</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>9.7782</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1.7125</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>d</mi>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{H_1}\\,{\\text{:}}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>H</mi>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>:</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp;data is not modeled by&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\\left( d \\right) = 9.7782{\\left( {1.7125} \\right)^d}\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>d</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>9.7782</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1.7125</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>d</mi>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>p-value = 0.893&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A2</strong></em></p>\n<p>Since 0.893 &gt; 0.05&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>R1</strong></em></p>\n<p>Insufficient evidence to reject <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{H_0}\">\n  <mrow>\n    <msub>\n      <mi>H</mi>\n      <mn>0</mn>\n    </msub>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>. So data is modeled by&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"n\\left( d \\right) = 9.7782{\\left( {1.7125} \\right)^d}\">\n  <mi>n</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>d</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>9.7782</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mo>(</mo>\n        <mrow>\n          <mn>1.7125</mn>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>)</mo>\n      </mrow>\n      <mi>d</mi>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[5 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"12144","referenceCode":"EXM.3.AHL.TZ0.9d.ii","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Perform a χ 2 goodness of fit test at the 5% significance level. You should clearly state your hypotheses, the p-value, and your conclusion.","paper":"3","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"d.ii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 5]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","SL 4.11—Expected, observed, hypotheses, chi squared, gof, t-test","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","AHL 4.13—Non-linear regression","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.5—Modelling functions","Topic 2—Functions","SL 2.6—Modelling skills","Topic 2—Functions","AHL 2.9—HL modelling functions"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}